data.meta_description: Stadium Australia is being redeveloped into a world-class 70,000-seat rectangular stadium, which will bring 46,000 seats closer to the action than ever before. The $810 million investment will deliver the ultimate customer and visitor experience, enabling NSW to attract and play host to the best events in the world.
